th the numbers to see how they impact margin of error.</p>
<p>If you want to learn how margin of error is calculated,&nbsp;<a href=3D"=
https://www.qualtrics.com/experience-management/research/margin-of-error/#_=
eswtswt4kryk">skip ahead to our breakdown of the margin of error formula</a=
></p>
<div class=3D"bg-gradient-135deg border-leaf col-lg-7 text-white white back=
ground-image pt-3 pb-5 ">
